listing_title: A fresh start and a great locale
listing_description:
The enduring appeal of Eltham's Woodridge Estate can be fully appreciated in this beautiful fully renovated family home, set amid native gardens and lovely eucalypts. 
The two-storey residence features wood flooring that flows seamlessly throughout an inviting lounge with adjoining dining room. The new kitchen/meals/living zone boasting stone benches, new quality stainless steel appliances and ample storage opening to an expansive deck area overlooking the established gardens.
Three robed bedrooms (master with walk-in robe and renovated ensuite), a bright luxurious central family bathroom and a good-sized study/fourth bedroom. 
A sunny rear deck is just right for outdoor entertaining and weekend relaxation, while the pretty rear garden has lots of room for kids to play and explore. 
Finishing touches include ducted heating, evaporative cooling, air conditioner, excellent storage, large laundry, sandpit and double carport. 
Add to this a tranquil Eltham locale with easy access to bus, parklands, Eltham East Primary School, central Eltham shops and train station.

Nestled within a sensational family setting, elite educational enclave and tranquil cul-de-sac, this weatherboard home captivates with its flexible floorplan of up to six bedrooms with open living. A serene lifestyle awaits with absolutely everything just moments away, yet perfectly set back off the main thoroughfare. It’s an easy meander to Mt Scopus Memorial College, Deakin University and the Presbyterian Ladies College, with a choice of golf, sporting and leisure clubs, buses, trams and major arterial roads and a plethora of cafes, dining and shopping from Burwood Heights and Burwood Bricks to nearby Forest Hill, The Glen and Chadstone Shopping Centres. The home itself offers enormous potential to be cutting edge in design with a vast accommodation, alfresco deck and a choice of rooms to repurpose to incorporate a home office, separate lounge or music room. Extras include timber flooring, two bathrooms, built-in robes, SS oven and gas cooktop, timeless timber kitchen cabinetry and a home of instant comforts and warmth.
